      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HERE TO PLAY (1) held a forward position from the pinch but began to paddle on the bend and drifted out of the finish when 5th at Warragul in Mix 6/7 company. Has claims if she runs up to expectations. DEL AMITRI (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (30.24) in a Mix 6/7 at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Likely to play a prominent role. SHE'S JUST FINE (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (26.09) in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win at Shepparton. Cannot be underestimated. ASTON MACQUARIE (2) has definite claims at his first try at this circuit.",
